buyerAgent.name: Trinity J. Keller - Top Producer with NOLA Living Realty

data.description: Beautifully maintained home situated on a corner lot in Plantation Estates. This charming ranch-style residence boasts a spacious living area with a brick fireplace and plenty of natural light. Kitchen hosts bar-style seating, ample cabinet and pantry storage, and granite countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen is the dining area that leads to the bonus room that is currently used as an office. Step outside to discover a covered patio area in the backyard, designed for easy maintenance and entertaining. Unique to this home is the converted 2-car garage, now a fantastic entertainment or movie room complete with a projector & screen! The large primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a second fireplace, abundant closet space, and an ensuite bath equipped with a separate shower, a relaxing tub, and dual sinks. Large laundry room that doubles as a half bath and counter space for a folding area. Brand new A/C (2024) Schedule your showing and make this amazing home yours!
